{"tid":2261724,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網紅花費36萬整型身材變得前凸後翹　後悔加工男人都被嚇走","createTime":"2020-10-28T14:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T03:11:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"085bc812b1d208e995d20727422937068a1d7e7b","tid":2261724,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"時下醫學美容技術發達，吸引不少女性「進廠維修」以致達到個人要求的最佳效果。而在德國方面就有一位網紅名叫Yvonne Bar的24歲女子，就非常沉迷整型手術，最終令自己變成一位擁有前凸後翹好身材的女人，不過近來她卻對整型一事感到非常後悔，事關她覺得好男人都被她嚇走了。<br />\n<br />\n據英國媒體《每日星報》指出，Yvonne Bar過去做了多種整型手術，包括豐胸﹑提臀等，一共花費超過3.6 萬英鎊（約36萬港元）。眼見Yvonne Bar對自己整完的身材似乎非常滿意，不時在社交網站上貼許多性感自拍照，但最近她卻因為男朋友的關係而想進行縮胸手術。事關，她的男朋友因為她胸前加工的關係拒絕同她一起出現公開場合，令她感到不開心。再者她亦覺得許多男人對她不認真，似乎好男人都被她嚇走。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，Yvonne Bar亦覺得豐胸完之後有後遺症，因為胸前的重量已經超過正常的負荷範圍，因此時常令她感到下背疼痛。"},{"pid":"b77b1de4be8730079f7998ab2eb693de4fd060c2","tid":2261724,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201028/398107432959610880640932.jpeg/Q416zQdPQMP5d5I5mTX4TJLmEual8fMp3x3E8d8dxPE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201028%2F398107432959610880640932.jpeg%2FQ416zQdPQMP5d5I5mTX4TJLmEual8fMp3x3E8d8dxPE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0fcb06c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201028/398107725499731968509648.jpeg/9YhV_WzjIM-DQDDEqpJIAhETUtlBj5k12xMAV9sTAFc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201028%2F398107725499731968509648.jpeg%2F9YhV_WzjIM-DQDDEqpJIAhETUtlBj5k12xMAV9sTAFc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=88ed294e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201028/398108973514887168607453.jpeg/KchBMBLNeM4lFXu0hEwV9EbkRhuDr4esybPyScmz8kk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201028%2F39